3 (2) Meet the following continuing education requirements:
4 a. Grade level II contractor: 3 hours per year.
5 b. Grade level IV contractor: 6 hours per year.
6 c. Point-of-sale inspector: 6 hours per year.
7 d. Authorized on-site wastewater evaluator: 12 hours per year.
8 e. Private compliance inspector: 12 hours per year.
9 f. For persons holding more than one certification issued by the Board,
